author: DO NOT WISH TO HAVE NAME INCLUDED WITH REVIEW
title: DO NOT WISH TO HAVE NAME INCLUDED WITH REVIEW
text:
New employee took me on the tour and filled out forms...had to go back a few days later to sign where he had overlooked. Space was clean and
appeared to be safe with lighting, codes, and such. When the experienced employee arrived on the day of moving into units, all went much better.
Professional service and friendliness from the beginning setting up an appointment by phone as well as day of tour and day of moving in. Prices comparable but not looking forward to increase in 6 months...bad experience in another state with similar storage.
